'''Piccalilli''' is a type of [[Cookbook:Pickle|pickle]] made from chopped up [[Cookbook:Vegetable|vegetables]] and hot [[Cookbook:Spices and herbs|spices]], especially [[Cookbook:Mustard|mustard]].

