== Previously strong verbs that are now irregular ==

Added (in brackets) the older forms of verbs that used to be strong, because I believe that helps in understanding why today's forms look the way they do, and why some irregular verbs have the ''-it'' suffix that is usually the sign of a strong verb. [[User:ClaesWallin|clacke]] 16:19, 22 February 2007 (UTC)

